Introduction

School Event Award System (SEAS) is a web application that provides information about School event and to the general public. This guide focuses on how to use the advanced features along with other tips for navigating the website.

Who should read this document? GATC’s Web developer,Web master, and eveyone who is interested and would like to learn more about the website features.

SEAS Search Features

SEAS provides many ways for users to find their events . The Advanced Search function is the most powerful search algorithm in the industry.

Manage Personal Event

There are two tables that allows users to manage their events.

My Events

My Events display all the current events for the future.

My Past Events

My past events display all the historical events that users have attend before.

There are two tables that allows users to manage their prizes.
